Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你不要再跟成瀨澪有任何牽連了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為她是准S級的監視對象嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.38,0:00:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已經知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.96,0:00:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然 村裏決定由你來監視她們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大致情況是從老爸那兒聽來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那為什麼還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明會讓刃更和迅先生都受到牽連的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.35,0:01:59.81,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{@\an3\fad(600,600)\blur1\pos(600,291)}「重逢與信賴的夾縫間」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.15,0:02:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到澪大人的同學裏邊居然有勇者一族的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.59,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也是沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.21,0:02:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是這麼容易被看穿的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不能勝任監視的工作啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當她說自己是刃更的青梅竹馬的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就該發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我居然還在班上宣稱我們正在同居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在都還覺得他們兩個是在幽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要對方不攻擊我們的話 就不用擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.24,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟我們沒有這個餘力去得罪勇者一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我擔心的並不是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我並不是在偷窺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是擔心刃更的人身安全而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.32,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.12,0:02:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才這種程度詛咒就已經發動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪因為週遭人們的企圖導致父母親被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在連她本人也被盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是想以一個普通女孩的身份活著而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此我決定了要保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我已經沒有像以前那樣的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然勇者一族無法保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無法為她而戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼這使命就一定該由我來完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您的找錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦啊 萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙竟然下了那麼大決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今後我該怎麼去面對刃更啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是好事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這證明了刃更真的是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人只要敞開心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更加信賴他就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的就這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有啊 這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果澪大人想做點什麼來回報刃更的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就去做做看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白柚希你的擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五年前的那件事 我沒能對自己做的事情負責到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對 刃更並沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我所犯下的錯也是不會消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不對 不管別人說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當時是刃更救了我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 澪她跟我不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她勇敢地面對過去 拚命想活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要奮戰到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我才想要保護她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洗澡什麼的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.40,0:05:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是這能讓她心情變好點就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不認為光憑刃更你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能夠擊敗盯上成瀨澪的魔族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它們的目標是沉睡於她身體內的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.27,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒必要贏 只要不輸就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.36,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.11,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不希望因為我們的戰鬥而牽連到你跟村裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.96,0:05:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是低級的迷失惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為受到成瀨澪魔王的力量所吸引而聚集過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.28,0:06:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果週遭因為成瀨澪的存在而陷入危險的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,村裏馬上會將她認定為必須消滅的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時候我不是會手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.35,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使那樣會被你怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}那咱們趕快吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然幽會到這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是會讓人感到有點不安的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我剛剛不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是什麼幽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懷疑刃更是不是跟那女人串通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說是吧 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然我們是相信刃更的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過 作為今後共同戰鬥的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們想要進一步加深這種信賴關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是這樣而已 你說是吧 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯 正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更你不也這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是這樣沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就知道你會這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是想讓我幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要想加深信賴關係的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有坦誠相見了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是男人之間的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像這樣一同去感受羞恥的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.99,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算不願意也會變得團結起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼鬼道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.13,0:07:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 澪大人就過來幫刃更擦背吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用啦 我自己來就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯把毫無防備的後背展現給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才能構築起信賴關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.32,0:08:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,估計也用了這套話哄騙了澪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼能輸給野中柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那我開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別動 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亂動的話 殺你一百次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做這種事 雖然好難為情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且還沒吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得買了蛋糕回來 差不多應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就猜到會這樣 所以拿進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請吧 刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 在浴室裏吃蛋糕是鬧哪樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.73,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這吃法也太新潮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然在洗澡的時候吃蛋糕難易度太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點沖乾淨就出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.94,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥難得買來的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不客氣指的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少也要把沒掉到地上的份給吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然對蛋糕也太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可真是美味 澪大人也來點怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 澪 難不成你也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們倆個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 你們既然有這種想法的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最後變成怎麼樣我可不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃…刃更哥 冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會好好回報你們哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.30,0:10:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了令這樣挑逗的行為不再發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,徹底令你們屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 全部是夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到中途為止都是現實哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥突然站了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.67,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卻猛地噴著鼻血倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 話說回來 刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.90,0:11:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多 該把手從我屁股上移開了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.90,0:11:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.21,0:11:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是我自己擅自鑽進刃更哥的被窩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 睡著的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.26,0:11:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠無意識地把手伸進女孩子的內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥居然這麼積極 還真讓我嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 畢竟能做出哪種夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢？難道剛才是你用魅魔的魔法讓我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是稍微偷看了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可是刃更哥自己做的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.08,0:11:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我自己？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒呀 不過居然看到那種夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.75,0:12:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定意外地擁有成為抖S鬼畜混蛋的潛質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 澪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來在照顧刃更哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但時間不早了 就讓她去睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是麼 那正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞 我有事情找你商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.41,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社團活動之後去哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之先去車站前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼嘛 睡得這麼安穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醒醒 小刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說你不用做暑假作業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我第二個學期才剛轉過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}也沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近上課也一個勁地睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點都在意人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再跟成瀨澪扯上關繫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 野中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老師讓你去辦公室一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 我也要去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.32,0:13:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是要讓你們兩個幫忙整理暑假作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為啥是我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真遺憾啊 小刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打算一個人輕鬆的話就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦 要打電話叫一下萬理亞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}我一個人也行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我身為班委的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟老師也交代了 我也來幫忙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣豈不是就像我不信任刃更了一樣麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下嘛 我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說 你的詛咒又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼…都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 澪 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪 澪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貧血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然還有點低燒 不過休息一下就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是傳聞中的轉校生麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轉學第一天開始 就和全校男生為敵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺怎麼樣啊 小帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老師們之間都聽到這種傳聞了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己完全沒有那個意思卻四處樹敵 該怎麼辦呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要找到更多的夥伴就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有這麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在全校男生都成了敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,問題不在數量 而是夥伴的質量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,質量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可不要把數量和質量分開來考量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}長谷川老師 請立刻到辦公室一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}通知再播送一遍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經這個時間了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 我得馬上去開個會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走的時候把門鎖上 之後再還我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.99,0:15:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是保健課的長谷川千里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,東城刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要好好分清敵我喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是奇怪的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪 沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒的效果還有殘餘麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託了 別讓我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但…但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 我會在你身邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都這麼說了 你就別用那種眼神看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 瀧川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很不好意思 我一時半會還回不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我會幫你弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也幫我跟柚希和老師說一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瀧川說會替我去做作業整理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何 好一點了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 稍微冷靜一點了 大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒只有在你打算做壞事的時候才會發動的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也…也沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 我去和萬理亞聯繫一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就再休息一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 萬理亞又去遊戲中心了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 她說最近有個比較沉迷的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 一個玩遊戲一個打瞌睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們倆也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和打瞌睡沒有關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會在你身邊的 別這麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣 可能會比較晚回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞭解 再等一下就去接你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.81,0:16:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後 你那邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天少見的沒有感覺到類似的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 那等一會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 是瀧川嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別一副看到怪物一樣的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你來替我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 比起那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成瀨沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還好吧 已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她突然就倒下了 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臉都紅了 好像還很害羞的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早晚會報答你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 小刃你見到野中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.42,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪了 她應該去看你們了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 停電嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道進到學校裏面來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野中柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有話和你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞…搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 小刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我閃開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.25,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 你要說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你從刃更那裏聽說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這個學校的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呢 聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什麼人 和那傢伙又是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你在一起會讓刃更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.00,0:18:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從刃更身邊離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該還沒有走遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因為我掉以輕心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙知道了所有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還說過要保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我們是一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果還是要來硬的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我也不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是在利用刃更的溫柔而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你又是在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無視那傢伙的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擅自將自己的溫柔強加給他不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會找借口 也不會後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「把刃更你捲進來真是抱歉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今說這種話太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我要堂堂正正的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和那傢伙一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔法防壁被……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說一次 我絕不饒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你知道刃更的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不可能說得出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更已經不能像以前那樣戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,單是拿起劍應該都很痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更在五年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把很多的同伴從這個世界消滅掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.91,0:20:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.14,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 不就是為了這種時候才做的主從契約嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.97,0:20:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迅先生和刃更離開了村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去了作為一族的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更現在也因為那個過去而痛苦著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓刃更拿起劍到底有多麼殘酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼可能會懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是怎麼回事 柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不應該是負責監視而已嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪 你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是說過不會敵對勇者一族嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.44,0:21:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正在說你的過去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到剛才為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被從勇者一族中放逐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還在保護前代魔王的遺孤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是讓人感興趣的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的魔族是你召喚的麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 你說魔族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今擔心也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近幾天他可是數次的揮劍戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.56,0:22:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到天亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.93,0:22:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙 很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 每晚都在戰鬥是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是為了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所繼承的前代魔王的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會招來迷失的低級惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.20,0:22:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果那些傢伙對人類造成危害的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.88,0:22:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇者一族也會把你看為危險的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.39,0:22:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把你從監視對像變為消滅對像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果庇護消滅對象的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.14,0:22:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算原本是勇者一族也難逃懲戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.21,0:22:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以她才會讓你離開他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是為了不會變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你身邊的夢魔和他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.45,0:23:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才會不分晝夜的在獵殺迷失了的惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.11,0:23:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.57,0:23:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.63,0:23:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 萬理亞不再來接我了也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.26,0:23:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果說了的話 澪就會責備自己對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.56,0:23:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.05,0:23:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.01,0:23:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.26,0:23:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 錯不在你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}不 成瀨澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一切都是你這個存在的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.82,0:23:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼受打擊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.74,0:23:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就把一切根源的前代魔王之力交出來如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.58,0:23:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趴下 澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次要連她也一起消除了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.44,0:23:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.49,0:23:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.27,0:23:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.34,0:24:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.76,0:24:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.82,0:25:46.30,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(320,310)\blur2.5}下集\N\N直至悲傷為零之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.31,0:00:50.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}堅信光明 追求希望
