Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Faraway 無論多麼遙遠都將握緊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.06,0:01:32.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}如果不願失去這份珍貴的思念的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:39.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Anyway 總應能靠著自己在這世上前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}向著未來奔去
